e.gravatar.com/avatar/ae49a13e365491709d29c1ff43b80e1d3599953d3655d0d0b04e376dc0420dd8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ae49a13e365491709d29c1ff43b80e1d3599953d3655d0d0b04e376dc0420dd8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yourmama/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">yourmama</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 28, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This company is <em>not </em>selling a Product. It is subscribing subscribers to Spider Webs, and the company is the Spider.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The Best Page Builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/k1mz/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ab05a82319ecb613b566285d1d86066b058bc953e1df10c03728e5655084ab1a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ab05a82319ecb613b566285d1d86066b058bc953e1df10c03728e5655084ab1a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/k1mz/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">keivan mahnazadeh <small>(k1mz)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 26, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Best Page Builder ♥</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I have the Pro Version --- support is worthless.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tiro0153/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/28d0024c93ecc2e541b7b7306d714eb2f9d92c7ba82d32e5e0822b387def9fe5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/28d0024c93ecc2e541b7b7306d714eb2f9d92c7ba82d32e5e0822b387def9fe5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tiro0153/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tiro0153</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 23, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Issue Reported to Support?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>In Elementor Pro, a styled button (with custom hover color) stays in its hover appearance after being clicked. It doesn\'t return to the normal state unless manually blurred or reset. Cache is set to default or inactive. No caching plugins. This appears to be a focus/hover conflict and shouldn’t require custom CSS or JavaScript.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If it requires CSS or JavaScript in order to resolve the issue then its a bug. Tier one support does not have a clue...all they want to do is access your site, and you better make sure that you have a good backup. In my case it should have gone to the developers. They wanted to get their 2 cents in . All they did was waste my time. I have been a customer of Elementor now for years and never did I run into such horrible customer service/support. There has to be a better page builder out there. When this one works it works really good. If you need support that is when it gets dicey.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Terrible Customer Service</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tgewebdev/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/65a0425a99837422d5dfac2290979c96ce8e75ff40adeaccabae83bc56cab8e8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/65a0425a99837422d5dfac2290979c96ce8e75ff40adeaccabae83bc56cab8e8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tgewebdev/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tgewebdev</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 22, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The plugin is good <em>as long as it\'s working</em>, but if something breaks good luck. <strong>You have 0 support</strong>. I went into my Elementor account thinking that because I have one site under their Pro license that maybe they could help me trouble shoot why the editing view and live view were not matching.<br />The technical support person kept pushing \"Pro\" subscription on me, when I told her repeatedly I don\'t want that. The Elementor plugin should work without me needing to upgrade. <br />60 mins later, no resolution, no help, just a run-around - The reps either lie or have comprehension issues, or maybe they just love wasting your time.<br />I am incredibly disappointed that such a big company like this has such terrible customer service. I think I\'m going to cancel my other Pro license since they clearly do not care about their customers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Careful with the subscription models</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artyberty/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/78f1e14ec59ed9f6be60a70a6b90beedc1520644d7e1dc39f67236a78b4477c5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/78f1e14ec59ed9f6be60a70a6b90beedc1520644d7e1dc39f67236a78b4477c5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/artyberty/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">artyberty</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 22, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The plug-in, regarding its functionalities is of great value. But you have to be very careful with which subscription you choose. They have multiple tiers and types and are absolutely unwilling to change one subscription to another if you realize you need additional features you did not book before. Their suggestion is just to book a new one and let the old one sit unused. Actual quote from their support:<br /><br />\"I highly suggest you to purchased your desire plan and let this Advanced Plan to expire.<br />That being said, you can purchase a new plan and simply reconnect it to the website.\"<br /><br />I never had this issue with any other Provider. They always upgraded plans when requested. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Must-Have Builder for Any WordPress User</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdsalimreza8790/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5da8e76fa1396fe81baab0d6880b95c8d8004a34962f6e45823f6cb12940acb7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5da8e76fa1396fe81baab0d6880b95c8d8004a34962f6e45823f6cb12940acb7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mdsalimreza8790/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mdsalimreza8790</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mai 15, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Elementor is a powerful, intuitive website builder that transformed how I design and deliver websites. Its drag-and-drop interface, flexible styling, and professional templates make it a must-have tool for growing any online business or portfolio.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The best...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andykbizzle/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/341b694adffdaf794028ab20b8f38d89409414b519cc674665ca57b30f87ad11?s=16&#038;d=mons